{"tid":52260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（有圖）用左380萬係沙田買左間村屋，發現⋯","createTime":"2016-12-24T02:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-24T05:46:14.000Z","uid":26703,"like":0,"dislike":127,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"be25ca6c40309ef0958b339d936b40143d02f2d0","tid":52260,"uid":26703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-24T02:17:47.000Z","msg":"前幾日買左沙田某村屋，380萬即買即入伙，包曬傢具，其實都算係咁，住左幾日成日夜晚都聽到廳有聲，但落到去又見唔到有乜野特別，初時以為係側邊d住戶嘈住曬，咁之後打探下原來左右都無人住，咁我就打電話去問下經紀上手係乜人住啦，之後個經紀話上手係一個外國人住左2年,最後因為要返英國所以搬走。<br />\n<br />\n咁夜晚返到屋企又聽到有聲，我未火都黎埋囉屌，搵左好耐之後發現d聲係廚房度傳出黎....<br />\n<br />\n我去到廚房搵到個門..我一推開後見到個洞..之後我入左去睇...發生見到咁既野...我影左好多相....好痴線<br />\n<br />\n我而家想搬...點算<br />\n<br />\n原link<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.twgreatdaily.com/cat99/node1380002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.twgreatdaily.com%2Fcat99%2Fnode1380002&d=OMw36nFn9ci1y3EsJSVXNEsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=66bd7676\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.twgreatdaily.com/cat99/node1380002</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/764v7TB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F764v7TB.jpg&h=f3a8b13e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/101524_1134708060ceff14658e6b573ea83223.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F101524_1134708060ceff14658e6b573ea83223.jpg&h=ec6b7ff6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/101525_ad9dd17543e1b631a085a51615776bab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F101525_ad9dd17543e1b631a085a51615776bab.jpg&h=4cb8a84a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/24/101526_ce02c57bbd835587df7dc57cb253683e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F24%2F101526_ce02c57bbd835587df7dc57cb253683e.jpg&h=c92d41e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src